\]for a quotient of $30_4$. Note that $12_4\div2_4=6_{10}\div2_{10}=3_{10}=3_4$. Now we find the product of $13_4$ and $30_4$. $$\begin{array}{@{}c@{\;}c@{}c@{}c@{}c@{}c@{}c}
& & & & \stackrel{2}{1} & 3_4& \\
& & & \times & & 3 & 0_4 \\
